<servinfosub id = "ASLAP70A6304016002">
<title>
Postup potvrdenia DTC
</title>
<topic id = "ASLAP70A6304016003">
<title>
DTC C1161
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Obráťte sa na Potvrdenie postupu pre DTC P0500 snímača rýchlosti vozidla “A”. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1104039"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</topic>
<topic id = "ASLAP70A6304016004">
<title>
DTC C1162
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Obráťte sa na Potvrdenie postupu pre DTC P0335 snímača polohy kľukového hriadeľa “A”. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1104033"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</topic>
